<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Многопроцессорные системы — Образовательный ресурс</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --accent: #68e383;
      --accent-dark: #3dba5a;
      --bg: #f5f5f5;
      --bg2: #ebebeb;
      --text: #111;
      --text-muted: #666;
      --radius: 15px;
      --header-h: 72px;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; cursor: none; }
    body { 
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; 
      background: var(--bg); 
      color: var(--text); 
      overflow-x: hidden;
      cursor: none;
    }

    /* ==========  КУРСОР ========== */
    .cursor-dot {
      position: fixed;
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
      transition: transform 0.1s ease, width 0.2s, height 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }
    .cursor-ring {
      position: fixed;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border: 2px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9998;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, width 0.2s, height 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    }
    .cursor-ring.hover {
      width: 65px;
      height: 65px;
      background: rgba(104, 227, 131, 0.15);
      border-color: var(--accent-dark);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    }
    .cursor-dot.hover {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      background: var(--accent-dark);
    }
    a, button, .btn, .card, .toc-item, .arch-card, .video-container, 
    .refs-list li, .conclusion-card, .nav a, .bottom-nav a, .logo,
    .timeline .tl-item, .info-box, .side-image {
      cursor: none;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    header {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
      height: var(--header-h);
      background: rgba(245,245,245,.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      transition: box-shadow .3s;
    }
    header.scrolled { box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px;
      height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
    .logo span { color: var(--accent); }
    nav { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    nav a {
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;
      padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 30px; transition: background .2s, color .2s;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    nav a:hover, nav a.active { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
    .burger { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; cursor: pointer; padding: 6px; }
    .burger span { display: block; width: 24px; height: 2px; background: var(--text); border-radius: 2px; transition: .3s; }

    /* PAGE SYSTEM */
    .page { min-height: 100vh; padding-top: var(--header-h); display: none; }
    .page.active { display: block; }

    /* MOVING TEXT */
    .marquee-wrap { overflow: hidden; background: var(--text); padding: 16px 0; }
    .marquee-track { display: flex; animation: marquee 30s linear infinite; width: max-content; }
    .marquee-track span { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; padding: 0 48px; white-space: nowrap; }
    .marquee-track span em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
    @keyframes marquee { from { transform: translateX(0); } to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - var(--header-h));
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 32px;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-subtitle-top { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .hero-title { font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hero-title em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 520px; }
    .btn-group { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn {
      padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; border: none; display: inline-block; transition: .2s;
    }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--text); color: #fff; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #333; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-outline { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 2px solid var(--text); }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--text); color: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* VIDEO CONTAINER */
    .video-container {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #0f0f1a);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
      transition: transform .3s, box-shadow .3s;
    }
    .video-container:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.3); }
    .video-container video, .video-container iframe {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
    .hero-video { min-width: 280px; }

    /* SECTIONS */
    .section { padding: 100px 32px; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-tag { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .section-title { font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 52px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .section-subtitle { font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: 60px; }

    /* CARDS */
    .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; }
    .card {
      background: #fff; border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      transition: transform .25s, box-shadow .25s;
    }
    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
    .card-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .card h3 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .card p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* SIDE IMAGE для архитектуры и типологии */
    .two-col-with-image {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .side-image {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .side-image:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    .side-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    .side-image-caption {
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      background: #fff;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    /* TOC ITEMS */
    .toc-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .toc-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 20px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      cursor: pointer; transition: .2s; background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .toc-item:hover { padding-left: 32px; background: var(--bg2); transform: translateX(4px); }
    .toc-item-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; }
    .toc-num { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); min-width: 32px; background: #e8f5e9; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .toc-name { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; }
    .toc-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; }
    .toc-arrow { color: var(--accent); font-size: 20px; transition: transform .2s; }

    /* TWO COL */
    .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: start; }
    .two-col-text p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; }

    /* TIMELINE */
    .timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .tl-item { display: flex; gap: 24px; padding-bottom: 40px; position: relative; }
    .tl-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 20px; top: 40px; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: var(--bg2); }
    .tl-item:last-child::before { display: none; }
    .tl-dot { width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; flex-shrink: 0; position: relative; z-index: 1; transition: transform .2s; }
    .tl-body h4 { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-top: 8px; }
    .tl-body p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* Стили для интерактивных элементов эволюции */
    .tl-item.interactive-evolution {
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .tl-item.interactive-evolution:hover {
      transform: translateX(8px);
    }
    .tl-item.interactive-evolution:hover .tl-dot {
      transform: scale(1.15);
      background: var(--accent-dark);
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(104, 227, 131, 0.5);
    }
    .tl-item.interactive-evolution:hover .evolution-year-title {
      color: var(--accent);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .tl-item.interactive-evolution {
      position: relative;
    }
    .tl-item.interactive-evolution::after {
      content: "🔍 Нажмите для просмотра";
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
      white-space: nowrap;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .tl-item.interactive-evolution:hover::after {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    /* Модальное окно для эволюции (без кнопки скачивания) */
    .evolution-modal {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85);
      z-index: 2000;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    }
    .evolution-modal-content {
      background: #fff;
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 90%;
      border-radius: 28px;
      position: relative;
      animation: modalFadeIn 0.3s ease;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    @keyframes modalFadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    }
    .evolution-modal-close {
      position: absolute;
      top: 18px;
      right: 24px;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 300;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: #999;
      z-index: 10;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .evolution-modal-close:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .evolution-modal-content h3 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 800;
      padding: 24px 28px 12px;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
      display: inline-block;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .evolution-modal-image-container {
      padding: 20px 28px;
      background: #f8f8f8;
      text-align: center;
    }
    #modalEvolutionImg {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: 350px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    .evolution-modal-desc {
      padding: 0 28px 28px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* ARCH CARDS */
    .arch-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .arch-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 20px; padding: 36px; border-left: 5px solid var(--accent); transition: transform .2s; cursor: pointer; }
    .arch-card:hover { transform: translateX(5px); }
    .arch-card h3 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .arch-card .arch-badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--accent); color: #111; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .arch-card p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* REFS */
    .refs-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
    .refs-list li {
      background: #fff; padding: 20px 24px; border-radius: 14px;
      font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6;
      display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
      transition: .2s; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .refs-list li:hover { box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.1); transform: translateX(4px); background: #f9f9ff; }
    .ref-num { font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent); font-size: 16px; min-width: 32px; cursor: pointer; }
    .ref-link { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; flex: 1; cursor: pointer; }
    .ref-link:hover { color: var(--accent-dark); text-decoration: underline; }

    /* CONCLUSION CARDS */
    .conclusion-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .conclusion-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: transform .2s; cursor: pointer; }
    .conclusion-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .conclusion-card::before { content: attr(data-num); font-size: 120px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent); opacity: .07; position: absolute; top: -20px; right: 10px; line-height: 1; }
    .conclusion-card h4 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .conclusion-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* BOTTOM NAV */
    .bottom-nav {
      background: var(--text); padding: 32px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .bottom-nav a {
      color: #aaa; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
      padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 30px; border: 1px solid #333;
      transition: .2s;
    }
    .bottom-nav a:hover, .bottom-nav a.active { background: var(--accent); color: #111; border-color: var(--accent); }

    .info-box { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px; border-left: 5px solid var(--accent); margin: 24px 0; cursor: pointer; transition: transform .2s; }
    .info-box:hover { transform: translateX(5px); }
    .info-box h4 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; }

    /* VIDEO UPLOAD */
    .video-upload {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .upload-btn {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #111;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: .2s;
      border: none;
    }
    input[type="file"] {
      display: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { display: none; }
      nav.open { display: flex; flex-direction: column; position: absolute; top: var(--header-h); left: 0; right: 0; background: #fff; padding: 16px; gap: 4px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
      .burger { display: flex; }
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .two-col-with-image { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .arch-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .conclusion-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .toc-item { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; }
      body { cursor: auto; }
      .cursor-dot, .cursor-ring { display: none; }
      .tl-item.interactive-evolution::after { display: none; }
    }
    .fadeIn, .fadeInLeft, .fadeInRight, .fadeInUp { animation-fill-mode: forwards; opacity: 0; }
    @keyframes fadeInUp2 { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(30px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes fadeInLeft2 { from { opacity:0; transform:translateX(-40px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateX(0); } }
    @keyframes fadeInRight2 { from { opacity:0; transform:translateX(40px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateX(0); } }
    .fadeIn { animation: fadeIn2 .7s ease forwards; }
    .fadeInLeft { animation: fadeInLeft2 .8s ease forwards; }
    .fadeInRight { animation: fadeInRight2 .8s ease forwards; }
    .fadeInUp { animation: fadeInUp2 .7s ease forwards; }
    @keyframes fadeIn2 { from { opacity:0; } to { opacity:1; } }
    .d1 { animation-delay: .15s; }
    .d2 { animation-delay: .3s; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor-dot"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring"></div>

<header id="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a class="logo" href="#" onclick="showPage('home')">МПС <span>●</span></a>
    <nav id="main-nav">
      <a href="#" onclick="showPage('home')" data-page="home" class="active">Главная</a>
      <a href="#" onclick="showPage('evolution')" data-page="evolution">Эволюция</a>
      <a href="#" onclick="showPage('architecture')" data-page="architecture">Архитектура</a>
      <a href="#" onclick="showPage('typology')" data-page="typology">Типология</a>
      <a href="#" onclick="showPage('software')" data-page="software">ПО</a>
      <a href="#" onclick="showPage('conclusion')" data-page="conclusion">Выводы</a>
      <a href="#" onclick="showPage('literature')" data-page="literature">Литература</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="burger" onclick="toggleMenu()"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
  </div>
</header>

<div id="modal" class="modal" style="display:none; position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8); z-index:2000; justify-content:center; align-items:center;">
  <div style="background:#fff; max-width:500px; padding:32px; border-radius:24px; position:relative;">
    <span onclick="closeModal()" style="position:absolute; top:16px; right:20px; font-size:28px; cursor:pointer;">&times;</span>
    <h3 id="modal-title">Информация</h3>
    <p id="modal-desc">Описание источника</p>
    <a href="#" id="modal-url" class="modal-link" style="margin-top:20px; display:inline-block; background:#68e383; padding:10px 24px; border-radius:40px; text-decoration:none; color:#111; font-weight:600;" target="_blank">Перейти к источнику</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== ГЛАВНАЯ ========== -->
<div id="page-home" class="page active">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="fadeInLeft">
        <div class="hero-subtitle-top">Образовательный ресурс</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Много<span><em>процессорные</em></span> системы</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">Изучение архитектур, эволюции и программного обеспечения для параллельных вычислений. Полное погружение в тему многопроцессорных вычислительных систем.</p>
        <div class="btn-group">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#" onclick="showPage('evolution')">Начать изучение</a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline" href="#toc">К содержанию</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fadeInRight d2 hero-video">
        <div class="video-container" id="homeVideoContainer">
          <video id="homeVideo" width="100%" controls style="border-radius: 20px; max-height: 300px; object-fit: cover;">
            <source src="введение.mp4" type="video/mp4">
          </video>
        </div>
        <div class="video-upload">
          <input type="file" id="homeVideoUpload" accept="video/*">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="marquee-wrap"><div class="marquee-track"><span>Многопроцессорные системы</span><span><em>·</em></span><span>Параллельные вычисления</span><span><em>·</em></span><span>SMP / NUMA / MPP</span><span><em>·</em></span><span>Архитектура ЭВМ</span><span><em>·</em></span><span>Классификация Флинна</span><span><em>·</em></span></div></div>

  <div id="toc" style="background: var(--bg2); padding: 60px 0;">
